# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Python FastAPI WebSocket Lab — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Splunk credentials come from the ROOT .env (../../.env).
# This file documents the lab-specific variables you also need.

# Shared (from root .env):
# SPLUNK_ACCESS_TOKEN=<your-ingest-token>
# SPLUNK_REALM=us1

# Lab-specific (export these or set in docker-compose.yml):
OTEL_SERVICE_NAME=fastapi-websocket-demo
OTEL_ENVIRONMENT=demo

# (Optional) Override OTLP endpoints
# OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_TRACES_ENDPOINT=https://ingest.us1.signalfx.com/v2/trace/otlp
# OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_METRICS_ENDPOINT=https://ingest.us1.signalfx.com/v2/datapoint/otlp
# OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_METRICS_ENDPOINT=https://ingest.us0.signalfx.com:443
